*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Descrição: Relatório de Clientes - ALV
*& Autor: João Paulo Candido da Silva
*& Data: 01/05/2022
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zclientes1700_alv.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Tables
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
TABLES kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Types / Structure
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_kna1,
         kunnr TYPE kna1-kunnr,
         name1 TYPE kna1-name1,
         ort01 TYPE kna1-ort01,
         regio TYPE kna1-regio,
         stras TYPE kna1-stras,
       END OF ty_kna1.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  WorkArea
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA: wa_kna1     TYPE ty_kna1,
      wa_fieldcat TYPE slis_fieldcat_alv.
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Internal Table
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
DATA: ti_kna1     TYPE TABLE OF ty_kna1,
      ti_fieldcat TYPE slis_t_fieldcat_alv.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Selection Screen
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
SELECT-OPTIONS s_kunnr FOR kna1-kunnr.

*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Start-Of-Selection - Evento
*&----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
START-OF-SELECTION.
* Open SQL ( Selecionando Dados )
  SELECT kunnr
         name1
         ort01
         regio
         stras
         FROM kna1
         INTO TABLE ti_kna1
         WHERE kunnr IN s_kunnr.

* Preenche o Fieldcat.
  wa_fieldcat-fieldname = 'KUNNR'.
  wa_fieldcat-tabname   = 'TI_KNA1'.
  wa_fieldcat-seltext_l = 'Codigo'.
  APPEND wa_fieldcat TO ti_fieldcat.
  CLEAR wa_fieldcat.

  wa_fieldcat-fieldname = 'NAME1'.
  wa_fieldcat-tabname   = 'TI_KNA1'.
  wa_fieldcat-seltext_l = 'Nome'.
  APPEND wa_fieldcat TO ti_fieldcat.
  CLEAR wa_fieldcat.

  wa_fieldcat-fieldname = 'ORT01'.
  wa_fieldcat-tabname   = 'TI_KNA1'.
  wa_fieldcat-seltext_l = 'Cidade'.
  APPEND wa_fieldcat TO ti_fieldcat.
  CLEAR wa_fieldcat.

  wa_fieldcat-fieldname = 'REGIO'.
  wa_fieldcat-tabname   = 'TI_KNA1'.
  wa_fieldcat-seltext_l = 'UF'.
  APPEND wa_fieldcat TO ti_fieldcat.
  CLEAR wa_fieldcat.

  wa_fieldcat-fieldname = 'STRAS'.
  wa_fieldcat-tabname   = 'TI_KNA1'.
  wa_fieldcat-seltext_l = 'Endereço'.
  APPEND wa_fieldcat TO ti_fieldcat.
  CLEAR wa_fieldcat.

* Mostrar o ALV
  CALL FUNCTION 'REUSE_ALV_GRID_DISPLAY'
    EXPORTING
      it_fieldcat = ti_fieldcat
    TABLES
      t_outtab    = ti_kna1.
